<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .error-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da 0%, #f5c6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">ðŸ’¥</div>
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>The server encountered an internal error and was unable to complete your request.</p>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>Error Details</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Status Code:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">500 Internal Server Error</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Request ID:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= requestId %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Timestamp:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= timestamp %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Error Type:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Simulated Server Error</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4>ðŸ§ª Testing Purpose</h4>
            <p>This is a simulated 500 error for testing error handling in the Printeer CLI. This endpoint always returns a 500 status code.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Use this endpoint to test error handling and retry logic in your CLI implementation.</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>